item.title: 【HD Live Performances】WEB-RiP - Taylor Swift - The Eras Tour, SoFi Stadium, Inglewood, CA, USA, 2023 [fixed song order + extra stereo track + bonus audio bootleg]
item.description:
I moved the 3 bonus songs (The Archer, Long Live, Wildest Dreams) where they belong among the other songs, without re-encoding the whole thing! I also added an extra stereo track converted from the main 5.1 audio. I dropped the disclaimer section. I also added very precise chapters for each song, a cover and an info file. The main tool I used was MKV Toolnix.

Bonus content: I made an audio bootleg with this entire show! (I split the tracks into songs, added tags, added cover).

This is an essential release for any pop fan. Credits to FLUX who recorded and shared this whole thing in the first place. Credits to Tay Tay and her team for making such an incredible show. Perhaps the biggest pop show of all time!
